WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.700 --> 00:00:03.100
Dad, don't you understand?

2
00:00:03.100 --> 00:00:05.000
As long as Lu Jinshenyi submits evidence

3
00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:06.900
You're going to jail for life.

4
00:00:06.933 --> 00:00:09.266
I can't bear to let you go, dad

5
00:00:10.733 --> 00:00:13.033
What is this money?

6
00:00:13.066 --> 00:00:14.433
I'm only here for a few decades.

7
00:00:14.600 --> 00:00:16.866
I will definitely make a comeback

8
00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:18.900
Hahahaha

9
00:00:21.366 --> 00:00:22.600
It's wonderful.

10
00:00:23.466 --> 00:00:24.633
What are you doing here?

11
00:00:26.133 --> 00:00:28.033
My wife and father-in-law are here

12
00:00:28.133 --> 00:00:29.233
I shouldn't have come

13
00:00:31.200 --> 00:00:33.200
Lu Jiancheng counts me as begging you

14
00:00:33.200 --> 00:00:35.033
Please spare my father once, okay?

15
00:00:35.300 --> 00:00:37.333
He and I are broke

16
00:00:37.333 --> 00:00:39.166
He has nothing left.

17
00:00:42.300 --> 00:00:44.366
Doesn't he still have a good daughter like you?

18
00:00:44.533 --> 00:00:47.866
Be careful, I see Xiaoyan's relationship is so good

19
00:00:48.333 --> 00:00:49.766
Father-in-law, I'm relieved

20
00:00:49.766 --> 00:00:51.600
It was my father-in-law who misunderstood

21
00:00:51.766 --> 00:00:53.033
Because of Xiaoyan

22
00:00:53.366 --> 00:00:56.133
If you are wronged, you will talk nonsense every day.

23
00:00:56.133 --> 00:00:57.700
Granny open mouth

24
00:00:58.066 --> 00:01:00.033
Mr. Open Mouth

25
00:01:00.466 --> 00:01:02.266
Can you give your father-in-law another chance?

26
00:01:02.266 --> 00:01:04.966
As long as you help me get through that difficult time

27
00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:07.666
I'll let him support you in everything from now on

28
00:01:12.666 --> 00:01:13.466
Dad?

29
00:01:13.900 --> 00:01:15.400
I want a divorce with the explanation

30
00:01:15.566 --> 00:01:16.833
Pardon me?

